      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, hematocrit, temperature) documented with uncertainty bounds traceable to calibrated instruments.",
      "rationale": "Flow rate and rotational speed are documented; hematocrit variability and temperature control records are absent from the experimental dataset. Test condition coverage is insufficient."
    },
