      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rel) applied to hemolysis index predictions versus experimental measurements across full operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Relative error metric applied at three operating points; the full operating envelope (five points) was not covered. Comparison is informative but incomplete relative to MRL 5 requirements."
    },
    {
