      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on a device geometry and operating regime that is representative of the target VAD COU, with documented similarity arguments.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry, which differs from the sponsor's proprietary VAD geometry. No formal similarity argument bridging the two geometries has been provided."
