      "acceptanceCriteria": "User influence on simulation outcomes assessed through inter-analyst variability study or structured sensitivity to user-controlled parameters.",
      "rationale": "No inter-analyst study was conducted. All simulations were run by a single analyst. User error contribution to prediction uncertainty is unquantified."
