      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty for the power-law hemolysis model quantified via Bayesian model comparison or alternative model ensemble; documented sensitivity to damage exponent selection.",
      "rationale": "The power-law exponents were taken from literature without systematic model form uncertainty analysis. Alternative hemolysis models (e.g., Giersiepen-Wurzinger) were not compared. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
