      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with probability distributions; global sensitivity analysis (e.g., Sobol indices) performed to rank input influence on NIH.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo sampling was performed but input distributions were assumed uniform without physiological basis. Sobol sensitivity analysis was not conducted. Input uncertainty characterization is incomplete."
