    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou2-dr-01",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all thirteen ASME V&V 40-2018 factors at Model Risk Level 5. While six factors remain unassessed and all assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels, the project sponsor assigned a low-risk decision tier based on the exploratory nature of the current submission phase. The team accepted the package under the ProfileMinimal conformance level, acknowledging that a full structured Context of Use has not been formally attached. The narrative description of clinical research application is considered sufficient for the current phase. A follow-on assessment at ProfileComplete is required before regulatory submission.",
